      "name": "Note: Google Gemini Chat Model"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Publish to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Log Published Posts (Airtable) · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2",
